title: 3.9.0.CR2: NoClassDefFoundError: io/quarkus/security/spi/runtime/SecurityEvent
body:

Note: I did not touch/set `quarkus.otel.security-events.enabled`.

### Expected behavior

No failure, works like with 3.8.2

### Actual behavior

QuarkusTests fail due to a missing class

### How to Reproduce?

_No response_

### Output of `uname -a` or `ver`

_No response_

### Output of `java -version`

17.0.10

### Quarkus version or git rev

_No response_

### Build tool (ie. output of `mvnw --version` or `gradlew --version`)

Maven 3.9.6
